window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Keep your enemies close...</p> <p>Victor is the killer who always delivers...for the right price. And Heloise Salvatierra, patron of Guatemala's largest cartel, is ready and willing to pay him just that to eliminate the competition: her sister. Heloise has been battling Maria for control of the cartel in an endless and bloody war. Now, Victor decides who survives. An easy job if it weren't for the sudden target on his back.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p> <p>...and their enemies closer.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p> <p>Victor's not the only one on the hunt. Someone else has Maria in the cross hairs and will do anything to get the kill. In the middle of cartel territory with enemies closing in from all sides, Victor must decide where to put the bullet before one is placed in his head....</p>"; 
